eam on each plate. Place 3 beignets on each plate. Divide salad between the plates. Dollop some coriander chilli pesto on the side, and garnish with pine nuts, coriander cress and sumac."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Beignets","content":["80 g unsalted butter, diced","150 g water","2 pinches fine sea salt","120 g plain flour","3 medium eggs","120 g courgettes, cut in pieces","½ ripe avocado, small, diced (5 mm)","1 fresh green chilli, large, thinly sliced","50 g spring onions sliced (1 cm)","2 Tbsp fresh coriander leaves","½ lime, finely grated zest and juice","1 pinch ground black pepper"]},{"title":"Coriander Chilli Pesto","content":["25 g fresh coriander, leaves and stalks","20 g Parmesan cheese, cut in pieces (2 cm)","40 g rapeseed oil","1 Tbsp toasted pine nuts","1 fresh green chilli, large, halved, deseeded","2 garlic cloves","½ lime, freshly squeezed juice only","1 pinch fine sea salt, or to taste","1 pinch ground black pepper, or to taste"]},{"title":"Feta Cheese Cream","content":["200 g feta cheese, cut in pieces","100 g plain yoghurt","100 g double cream","1 pinch fine sea salt, or to taste","1 pinch ground black pepper, or to taste"]},{"title":"Courgette and Avocado Salad","content":["1 courgette, green, small, cut in thin strips with a vegetable peeler","1 courgette, yellow, small, cut in thin strips with a vegetable peeler","1 ripe avocado, small, diced (1 cm)","1 lime, juice and finely grated zest","1 Tbsp rapeseed oil","1 pinch fine sea salt, or to taste","1 pinch ground black pepper, or to taste"]},{"title":"Cooking and Serving","content":["sunflower oil, for deep frying","2 Tbsp toasted pine nuts, roughly chopped","coriander cress, for garnishing","sumac, for sprinkling"]}],"id":"r121157","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-v-Zc7cV-ElY\/XZMt2_PyWMI\/AAAAAAAAZ-U\/zk_rHYJkNMsiEDXCWPkF-mJxQMXiaRgggCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_2Tc9piZc-dOXNdxu.png","title":"Courgette and Avocado Beignets with Feta Cream, Coriander Chilli Pesto and Salad","publishedAt":"20